<div class="card card-custom gutter-b cb-card">
    <div class="card-header border-0 pt-6">
        <div class="card-title">
            <div>
                <h3 class="card-label font-weight-bolder mb-1">İşlem penceresi / No-trade hours</h3>
                <div class="text-muted font-size-sm">Düşük likidite, haber akışı veya ekip dışı zamanlar için işlem açmama penceresi foundation alanı.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-toolbar">
            <label class="checkbox checkbox-outline checkbox-outline-2x checkbox-primary mb-0">
                <input type="checkbox" checked id="cb_risk_notrade_toggle" data-cb-risk-notrade-toggle />
                <span></span>
                Aktif
            </label>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body pt-2" id="cb_risk_notrade_body">
        <div class="cb-form-grid">
            <div>
                <label class="cb-form-label">Başlangıç saati</label>
                <input type="time" value="22:00" class="form-control cb-form-control" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <label class="cb-form-label">Bitiş saati</label>
                <input type="time" value="01:30" class="form-control cb-form-control" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <label class="cb-form-label">Timezone</label>
                <select class="form-control cb-form-control">
                    <option>UTC placeholder</option>
                    <option>Europe/Berlin placeholder</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div>
                <label class="cb-form-label">Özet</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_risk_notrade_summary" value="22:00 - 01:30 arası yeni giriş kapalı" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cb-helper-text mt-3">Aktif olduğunda botlar sinyali görse bile yeni giriş açmama kuralı uygulanacakmış gibi düşünülür.</div>
        <div class="cb-chip-group cb-chip-group-sm mt-4">
            <button type="button" class="cb-chip is-active">Pzt</button>
            <button type="button" class="cb-chip is-active">Sal</button>
            <button type="button" class="cb-chip is-active">Çar</button>
            <button type="button" class="cb-chip is-active">Per</button>
            <button type="button" class="cb-chip is-active">Cum</button>
            <button type="button" class="cb-chip">Cts</button>
            <button type="button" class="cb-chip">Paz</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
